===Etymology===
Same word as {{och-l|繹|to unravel}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). See there for more.

Alternatively, {{zh-ref|Blažek and Schwarz (2017)}} suggest that this is perhaps a loan from a hypothetical {{bor|zh|ine-toc}} compound {{m|und|*klyælylyæ-yäkwæ||standing of horses}}, but this seems to be highly speculative.

The Taiwanese Hokkien sense is an {{obor|nan-hbl|ja|-|nocap=1}} {{ja-r|駅|えき}}.

